message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "Abir-Guard: Quantum-Resilient Agentic Vault for AI Agent Memory"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Maheshwari
    given-names: Abir
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0000-0000-0000"
    affiliation: "Aquilldriver"
abstract: >
  Abir-Guard is a quantum-resistant encryption vault designed for AI agent memory.
  It implements NIST-standard Post-Quantum Cryptography (PQC) using ML-KEM-1024
  and X25519 hybrid key encapsulation with AES-256-GCM envelope encryption to protect
  sensitive agent data from Harvest Now, Decrypt Later (HNDL) attacks.
